import datetime

d = datetime.datetime.now().time()
morning = datetime.time(9,0,0)
daytime = datetime.time(17,30,0)
night = datetime.time(22,0,0)

if d < morning:
	print 'üåÖ'
elif morning <= d < daytime:
	print 'üë∑'
elif daytime <= d < night:
	print 'üç∫'
else:
	print 'üí§'
